profile: Operating throughout Southern Ontario, Ontario Mould Specialists (OMS) can remediate any mould problems you face. Whether you have a residential, commercial or industrial mould issue, we perform guaranteed mould remediation services and restore structures to a healthier state to increase their market value. We offer full service of Indoor Air Quality Testing. We also are certified in Asbestos Abatement and Testing.
